A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Reverend Darion Hutcherson upon being named the 2025
2 Counselor of the Year by the Atlanta Public School System; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, a proper quality education for the young people of this state is the single most
4 important objective of the General Assembly; and
5 WHEREAS, Reverend Darion Hutcherson has been named the 2025 Counselor of the Year
6 by the Atlanta Public School System in recognition of his decades of outstanding service,
7 commitment, and leadership in the field of education; and
8 WHEREAS, on Thursday, March 27, 2025, the Atlanta Public School System will host a
9 special program in honor of Reverend Hutcherson to celebrate his achievements and present
10 him with this well-deserved tribute; and
11 WHEREAS, he is a firm believer that "all children can learn," a philosophy that has driven
12 his decades of impactful service to students across Georgia, Louisiana, South Carolina, and
13 the nation; and
