14 WHEREAS, the fruits of his labor include numerous professional athletes, doctors, lawyers,
15 elected officials, public servants, educators, and members of the United States Armed Forces
16 who carry forward the values and discipline instilled through his guidance; and
17 WHEREAS, his unwavering devotion to the children of the City of Atlanta, Fulton County,
18 the State of Georgia, and the nation has earned him the admiration and respect of peers,
19 students, and communities alike; and
20 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that this remarkable individual be
21 appropriately honored during this special time.
22 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
23 recognize and commend Reverend Darion Hutcherson, the 2025 Counselor of the Year, for
24 his decades of exemplary service in education and youth development as well as extend best
25 wishes for continued success.
26 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
27 to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to Reverend Darion
28 Hutcherson.
